message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music computing. cs.AI is also likely as it deals with machine learning and artificial intelligence. cs.SY is another possible category as it deals with control systems, which is relevant to the inverse control task. cs.LG is also possible as it deals with deep learning, which is used in this work. cs.MM is less likely as it deals with multimedia, which is not the main focus of this paper.
